		<p>@Aussie Aussie Aussie Oi Oi Oi!!!</p>
<p>Greatest sporting nation per capita on the face of the Earth?  Bollocks.<br />
Take a look at the figures posted here: <a href="http://www.symworld.com/medals" rel="nofollow">http://www.symworld.com/medals</a><br />
Gold Medals per capita leaves Australia ranked 7th behind countries with a fraction of your population.  Taking GDP into account leaves Australia lanquishing in a miserable 24th.  Well done to all Australian Athletes, but to call Australia&#8217;s elite sport funding &#8216;paltry&#8217; is a huge insult to the many smaller nations that managed amazing results with a mere fraction of the budget of Australia.</p>

